Contemporary design has a beautiful foyer that opens up into large living room with a gorgeous kitchen. lots of updates throughout, brand new HVAC. Tile in wet areas , hardwood floors, large backyard fully fenced, level yard with shade and gorgeous set up with extra concrete patio for firepit entertainment. Updated photos coming soon.
